  description: "asyncio.InvalidStateError.__name__.__len__() == 17 — asyncio.InvalidStateError.__name__ is 'InvalidStateError' (17 chars); this ties with LimitOverrunError.__name__.__len__()==17 (both are 17 chars); IncompleteReadError.__name__ is the longest at 19; QueueEmpty=10 and QueueFull=9 are shorter; InvalidStateError.__module__=='asyncio.exceptions' (len=18); InvalidStateError.__bases__[0].__name__=='Exception' (len=9); __mro__.__len__()==4; __doc__.__len__()==43; NEW in extra146: first standalone InvalidStateError name length invariant; verified with Python 3.14.3 on macOS/Darwin 25.4.0, 2026-04-11"
  category: identity
  kind: python_call_eq
  function: asyncio.InvalidStateError.__name__.__len__
  args: []
  expected: 17

